OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting with areas of cloud
OL,6,Fand perhaps a few light showers. Then
OL,7,Fbecoming dry with some bright spells,
OL,8,Fbefore cloud increases. Patchy light
OL,9,Frain may reach western areas by late
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain this evening, clearing
OL,13,Feast by the early hours. Large amounts
OL,14,Fof cloud and showers or longer spells
OL,15,Fof rain will follow, perhaps locally
OL,16,Fheavy. Milder than previous nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
