OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FStarting with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain, possibly heavy
OL,7,Fat times, mainly across eastern areas.
OL,8,FDrier and brighter conditions then
OL,9,Fspread follow, along with scattered
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fsunshine and scattered sometimes heavy
OL,14,Fshowers. Rain and strong winds arrive
OL,15,Fovernight, clears Tuesday with windy
OL,16,Fconditions and showers following.
OL,17,FWednesday breezy still, bright spells
OL,18,Fand isolated showers, warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
